I always thought it was interesting how Star Tropics 2 uses the $4011 reg to control the triangle volume.  I just wonder if there's obscure details like that in the programmer docs, or just in some kind of notes we'll never see.<br /><br />But yeah, I think all of us here collectively know more about the NES chips than probably the individuals who designed the things, heh.<br /><br />But for the service manual, there should be plenty more of those around.  Nintendo Service Centers used to be everywhere, in big department stores and stuff.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=10">Memblers</a> — Thu Jan 18, 2007 3:10 pm</p><hr />
